The &lt;a href="European%20Water%20Polo%20Championship"&gt;1997 Men's European Water Polo Championship&lt;/a&gt; was the 23rd edition of the bi-annual event, organised by the Europe's governing body in aquatics, the &lt;a href="Ligue%20Europ%C3%A9enne%20de%20Natation"&gt;Ligue Européenne de Natation&lt;/a&gt;. The event took place in &lt;a href="Seville%2C%20Spain"&gt;Seville, Spain&lt;/a&gt; from August 13 to August 22, 1997, as an integrated part of the &lt;a href="European%20LC%20Championships%201997"&gt;European LC Championships 1997&lt;/a&gt;.
